iety.com/2017/film/news/jurassic-world-sequel-danielle-pineda-the-detour-1201967088/|archive-date=2017-01-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隔月，[[泰德·拉文|泰德·拉文]]及[[詹姆斯·克伦威尔|詹姆士·克倫威爾]]雙雙以未知角色參演電影<ref name=Levine>{{cite news|last=Kroll|first=Justin|title='Jurassic World' Sequel Adds 'Silence of the Lambs' Actor Ted Levine|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/news/jurassic-world-sequel-ted-levine-1201984206/|accessdate=2017-02-10|work=Variety|date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211034450/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/jurassic-world-sequel-ted-levine-1201984206/|archive-date=2017-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Cromwell>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/james-cromwell-joins-jurassic-world-sequel-976841|title=James Cromwell Joins 'Jurassic World' Sequel (Exclusive)|date=2017-02-16|accessdate=2017-02-17|website=The Hollywood Reporter|last=Kit|first=Borys|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216225642/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/james-cromwell-joins-jurassic-world-sequel-976841|archive-date=2017-02-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[黃榮亮|黃榮亮]]則確認回歸飾演吳·亨利博士<ref name=Wong>{{cite news|last=Schwerdtfeger|first=Connor|title=Jurassic World 2 Is Bringing Back A Favorite Character|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1626659/|accessdate=2017-02-19|work=CinemaBlend.com|date=2017-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220092432/http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1626659/|archive-date=2017-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月，貝耶納宣布，出演過他先前每一部電影作品的演員{{link-en|潔洛汀·卓別林|Geraldine Chaplin}}已加盟劇組<ref name=Chaplin/>。4月25日，宣布《[[侏羅紀公園|侏羅紀公園]]》及《[[侏羅紀公園：失落的世界|侏羅紀公園：失落的世界]]》的演員[[傑夫·高布倫|傑夫·高布倫]]將回歸繼續飾演伊恩·馬康姆一角<ref name=Goldblum />。

